name: Igo-detector
tagline: Auto camera capture based facial detection
body:
Auto camera capture based facial detection

**Requirement**

* O/S : windows xp, windows 7 (32bit).
* Software : https://www.java.com/en/download/
* Hardware : webcam or standart camera (usb)

Untuk melihat file hasil capture, klik refresh atau tekan tombol F5 (keyboard) pada folder aplikasi IGO detector berada (windows explorer).
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
